- Locate the themes folder in wp-content folder of your Wordpress.org folder
- Go to underscores.me and generate a starter theme
- Download and then unzip it in the themes folder
- Activate the generated theme in your wordpress dashboard, All the styles should be stripped
- Open the generated theme folder with your chosen text editor, VS is used in these notes
- The index.php file combines together the header.php, a loop of content.php files and then our footer.php file at the bottom.
- Go to index.php and delete getsidebar() from code
- Go to content.php and comment out posted on and posted by.
- In Content.php, header.php, and footer.php delete whatever code you need. Mostly all of it if you want to start from scratch.
